<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("../partials/navbar") %>
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-10">
            <!-- Heading -->
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-700 sm:text-4xl">About This System</h1>
                <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg">Learn more about what this college management system is and how it
                    helps.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- System Overview -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-4">What is XYZ College Management System?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    The XYZ College Management System is a web-based platform designed to simplify the management of
                    academic and administrative tasks in colleges and universities. Built using Node.js, EJS, Tailwind
                    CSS, and Sequelize (SQL), it provides a centralized dashboard for managing students, teachers,
                    courses, attendance, exams, and more.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Features List -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700">👨‍🎓 Student Management</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Add, update, and manage student details, roll numbers, departments,
                        and more.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700">👩‍🏫 Teacher Management</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Maintain teacher profiles, subject assignments, and performance data.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700">📚 Courses & Subjects</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Create, assign, and organize academic courses and subjects by semester
                        or stream.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700">📈 Attendance & Exams</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Record attendance, schedule exams, and manage student results easily.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Technologies Used -->
            <div class="mt-10 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-4">🛠️ Technologies Used</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li><strong>Node.js</strong> – Server-side backend</li>
                    <li><strong>Express.js</strong> – Web framework</li>
                    <li><strong>EJS</strong> – Template rendering engine</li>
                    <li><strong>Sequelize ORM</strong> – SQL database modeling</li>
                    <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> – Frontend styling</li>
                    <li><strong>MySQL / PostgreSQL</strong> – Database system</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include("../partials/footer") %>
</body>

</html>